query: SELECT DISTINCT t.codigo, e.tipoEvento, COUNT(bg.id) as qtd_grupos FROM turmas t INNER JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id INNER JOIN briefing_grupo bg ON bg.eventoId = e.id GROUP BY t.codigo, e.tipoEvento ORDER BY t.codigo;
